In environment H : forall l m : lb, ⟦ l ++ m ⟧ = ⟦ l ⟧ + power (length l) 2 * ⟦ m ⟧ l, m : lb Unable to unify "⟦ l ⟧ + ⟦ m ⟧" with "⟦ l ⊕ m ⟧".

original: rewrite lb_nat_app with (l := l) (m := m). reflexivity.
